.SH NAME
.PP
git unstow
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
git unstow - restore the workspace state
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
git unstow is a helper alias to restore the workspace state.
.SH EXAMPLES
.IP \[bu] 2
\f[C]git unstow\f[R]
.SH SEE ALSO
